        "synopsis": {
            "value": "The drama follows Ra Eun Ho, an 18-year-old girl with dreams of becoming a webtoon artist, as she struggles in a school that discriminates based on wealth and academic performance. When she's wrongly framed as the legendary Student X, a mysterious troublemaker, her future is threatened. Alongside Hyun Tae Woon, the aloof son of the school's director, who has a troubled past, they form an unlikely alliance. As their relationship grows, they\n\njoin forces with other students to challenge the corrupt school system and bring about change.",
